            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1089944842" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1089944842" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1089944842">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fnx19920408/">kaoru</a>
                    <span>2016-10-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">科举和丁忧的废除切断了中央和地方的联系，毛的革命是为了扭转这种局面和尝试走东亚传统模式的最后一次尝试。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1085894824">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1085894824" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1085894824" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1085894824">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ruawas/">七七|不言</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-09-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">辛亥革命成功结束了中央政权对地方上流阶层权力的掣肘。实际上革命队伍里永远充满了机会主义者，急于分享权力爆炸后的碎片。所以除了观点不很出奇出新，地方视角和行文表述都很好。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

    </div>
