    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/15472/" target="_blank">凤凰文库·海外中国研究丛书——江苏人民出版社</a>
                <span class="pl">(彼岸)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/100338/" target="_blank">加州大学近代中国历史研究文献（中译本）目录</a>
                <span class="pl">(benshuier)</span>
